  "instructions": [
    "1. In a small bowl, whisk together sake, soy sauce, sugar, ginger, and garlic.",
    "2. Add sliced beef to the marinade and let it sit for at least 30 minutes.",
    "3. Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "4. Thread the marinated beef onto skewers.",
    "5. Grill the beef for 3-4 minutes per side, or until cooked to desired doneness.",
    "6. Transfer the beef to a plate and let it rest for a few minutes.",
